ShareVendor DetailsVisit the full company profile of Consolidated Edison Company Of New York, Inc..Consolidated Edison Company Of New York, Inc. 

sales volume (Estimated)$10,328,000,000 United States dollarsyear founded1884total employees13200employees at this location170


Overview Consolidated Edison Company Of New York, Inc. is an electric service company in New York. This private company was founded in 1884. With 71 other locations, the organization is a member of a large, complex corporate structure.Revenue The organization generates $10.3B in estimated sales.Employees Consolidated Edison Company Of New York, Inc. employs 13,200 people of which 170 employees are estimated to work at this location. In New York, an average company has between 3 and 352 employees, meaning that Consolidated Edison Company Of New York, Inc. employs a typical amount of people.
 





